- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is likely because the paper discusses the integration of Answer Set Programming (ASP) into software development, which is a subfield of AI.
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is also likely because the paper discusses the use of OOASP to support the software development process during design and testing.
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possibility because the paper discusses the integration of logic programming (ASP) with object-oriented programming.
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is also a possibility because the paper discusses the use of logic programming (ASP) to reason about object-oriented software models.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is less likely but still possible because the paper discusses the use of ASP to verify and transform instantiations of object models at runtime, which could potentially involve machine learning techniques.
